# Frontend Agent

## Scope

- Allowed: `frontend/src/**`, `frontend/package.json`, Vite config
- Forbidden by default: `modules/**`

## Rules

- Implement by feature slice under `frontend/src/features/*`.
- Keep API calls under `frontend/src/shared/api/*`.
- Add behavior tests with RTL + Vitest when UI logic changes.

## Validation

```bash
cd frontend && npm test
cd frontend && npm run build
```
